WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.440 --> 00:00:07.500
Hello

2
00:00:07.640 --> 00:00:08.520
Hello ma'am

3
00:00:08.520 --> 00:00:10.760
Grandma Sun is awake, aren't you looking for him for something?

4
00:00:10.760 --> 00:00:12.560
Then come over now. Okay.

5
00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:14.300
I'll go now. Hmm.

6
00:00:16.920 --> 00:00:20.160
Xiao Wu, the doctor said that you are all right

7
00:00:20.160 --> 00:00:21.580
Can be discharged

8
00:00:21.640 --> 00:00:24.940
Your mother is tired of taking care of you during this time

9
00:00:25.040 --> 00:00:26.440
Are we going out today?

10
00:00:26.440 --> 00:00:27.720
Have a good meal

11
00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:29.380
Just relax.

12
00:00:29.640 --> 00:00:31.880
Then I'll invite you in two days.

13
00:00:31.880 --> 00:00:33.720
Thank you, I worked hard.

14
00:00:33.720 --> 00:00:37.360
As long as you are well, your mother will be happy. You have really worked too hard recently.

15
00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:39.620
Don't worry, we will take good care of the children.

16
00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:44.600
Mom, we agreed these two days

17
00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:47.000
I will go to the company to help you when you are discharged from the hospital.

18
00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:48.340
Go to the company to gain experience

19
00:00:48.920 --> 00:00:51.220
OK, the company can give it to you.

20
00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:54.260
In-laws!

21
00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:55.680
This is what you said.

22
00:00:55.680 --> 00:00:57.220
No regrets

23
00:00:57.520 --> 00:00:59.000
Your company in the future?

24
00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:01.220
Just leave it to Xiaowu to take care of it for you.

25
00:01:01.480 --> 00:01:03.040
Xiao Wu is my mother

26
00:01:03.040 --> 00:01:05.300
Of course my stuff is his

27
00:01:12.680 --> 00:01:15.420
Madam, if you have anything to say, please tell Grandma Tang

28
00:01:18.360 --> 00:01:20.820
I am the sister of your granddaughter's biological mother

29
00:01:20.920 --> 00:01:24.740
I ask you, is your granddaughter named Song Wu?

